  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What starts as a routine investigation soon turns into a descent into darkness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They call him <strong>Manivore</strong>. More than just a killer… He is cold-blooded, intelligent, and manipulative. He doesn’t just kill his victims; he erases their traces, dismembers them, and leaves behind nothing but a grotesque work of art. For him, death is not an escape but the final piece of a meticulously crafted puzzle. And now, you are part of that puzzle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PHOTOGRAPH THE EVIDENCE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your camera to identify clues and evidence at the crime scene. Some truths cannot be seen with the naked eye.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/c43bdf1c8c6adfccfb4a39b32423fddd.poster.avif?t=1768336363\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/c43bdf1c8c6adfccfb4a39b32423fddd.webm?t=1768336363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/c43bdf1c8c6adfccfb4a39b32423fddd.mp4?t=1768336363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SOLVE PUZZLES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your mind and the clues around you to unravel the mysteries and uncover the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/9630272b66b2fc3bcdc80e52cae25186.poster.avif?t=1768336363\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/9630272b66b2fc3bcdc80e52cae25186.webm?t=1768336363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/9630272b66b2fc3bcdc80e52cae25186.mp4?t=1768336363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STAY ALERT TO SURVIVE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Listen to every sound, someone might be watching you. Watch your every step.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/2c804cf85cbd25870d0c33b2ff25ce57.poster.avif?t=1768336363\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/2c804cf85cbd25870d0c33b2ff25ce57.webm?t=1768336363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/2c804cf85cbd25870d0c33b2ff25ce57.mp4?t=1768336363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Photo Capture Mechanic</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Realistic Graphics</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>High-Quality Sound Design</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Variety of Puzzles</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>If you don’t want to end up on his table, play by his rules.</i></strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What starts as a routine investigation soon turns into a descent into darkness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They call him <strong>Manivore</strong>. More than just a killer… He is cold-blooded, intelligent, and manipulative. He doesn’t just kill his victims; he erases their traces, dismembers them, and leaves behind nothing but a grotesque work of art. For him, death is not an escape but the final piece of a meticulously crafted puzzle. And now, you are part of that puzzle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PHOTOGRAPH THE EVIDENCE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your camera to identify clues and evidence at the crime scene. Some truths cannot be seen with the naked eye.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/c43bdf1c8c6adfccfb4a39b32423fddd.poster.avif?t=1768336363\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/c43bdf1c8c6adfccfb4a39b32423fddd.webm?t=1768336363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/c43bdf1c8c6adfccfb4a39b32423fddd.mp4?t=1768336363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SOLVE PUZZLES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your mind and the clues around you to unravel the mysteries and uncover the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/9630272b66b2fc3bcdc80e52cae25186.poster.avif?t=1768336363\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/9630272b66b2fc3bcdc80e52cae25186.webm?t=1768336363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/9630272b66b2fc3bcdc80e52cae25186.mp4?t=1768336363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STAY ALERT TO SURVIVE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Listen to every sound, someone might be watching you. Watch your every step.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/2c804cf85cbd25870d0c33b2ff25ce57.poster.avif?t=1768336363\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/2c804cf85cbd25870d0c33b2ff25ce57.webm?t=1768336363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601980/extras/2c804cf85cbd25870d0c33b2ff25ce57.mp4?t=1768336363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Photo Capture Mechanic</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Realistic Graphics</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>High-Quality Sound Design</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Variety of Puzzles</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>If you don’t want to end up on his table, play by his rules.</i></strong></p>",
